comments.body:
I have compared to PostgreSQL output:
```sql
maxim=# select date_part('epoch', interval '1010 year 9 month 8 day 7 hour 6 minute 5 second 4 millisecond 3 microseconds');
    date_part
-----------------
 31897220765.004
(1 row)
```
It seems PostgreSQL just looses the precision.
